WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.667
Your joy spills into me like gold through cracked glass.

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:11.900
Someone’s grief blooms here, blue and unbearable, wearing my name.

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:18.033
Every heartbeat in the room drums beneath my skin at once.

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:24.767
I open my mouth, and a thousand feelings become weather.

